Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.45,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}I don't know what I should do now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.62,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}With every strength I can take to break enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:25.30,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}絶縁體のような表情で　抵抗を嫌う口実を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:29.56,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}共振拒む理由なんて　単純すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.61,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:47.16,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}I won't let you down come along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.91,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Taking back my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.62,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.88,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}確信はその手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:03.17,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}I'm waiting for till the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.68,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Taking back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.93,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}錆付いた意志でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.31,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Just change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:14.98,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}革命に似た Calling back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.19,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Tell me what's wrong with the society
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.19,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}that everybody is saying OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.99,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Low resistance of high zest inner cells
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.03,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}Rebuild the coil there is no lie
Comment: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.45,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}我现在该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.62,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}明明有了一切击败敌人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:25.30,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}你露出绝缘体般的表情 说着不愿抵抗的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:29.56,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}但拒绝共振的理由 却太过单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.61,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}为何不尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:47.16,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}我不会让你失望 随我前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.91,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}我要夺回我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.62,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}为何不尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.88,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}信心就在你的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:03.17,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}我会等待 直到黎明破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.68,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}夺回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.93,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}即便意志已然锈蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.31,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}只是改变这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:14.98,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}革命一般 回收一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.19,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}这个社会究竟怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.19,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}大家为何习以为常？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.99,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}高功率内细胞的低电阻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.03,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0}重建构线圈 让一切谎言烟消云散
